OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F303A1777680175
OL,3,CPeter Kay ushered off stage and
OL,4,Caudience evacuated after suspicious
OL,5,Cbag found
OL,7,FComedian Peter Kay was ushered off
OL,8,Fstage mid-performance and the audience
OL,9,Fwas evacuated after a "potential
OL,10,Fsuspicious bag" was found.
OL,12,FPolice said a 19-year-old man is being
OL,13,Fheld after the show at the Utilita
OL,14,FArena in Birmingham was halted on
OL,15,FFriday evening.
OL,17,FWitnesses said that two members of
OL,18,Fstaff came onto the stage about 45
OL,19,Fminutes into the performance,
OL,20,Fwhispered into Kay's ear, and then
OL,21,Fescorted him off.
OL,26,@qD@WOUrD@OO]
