OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F303A1777680175
OL,3,CPeter Kay ushered off stage and
OL,4,Caudience evacuated after suspicious
OL,5,Cbag found
OL,7,FSteve Aspinall, who was at the gig
OL,8,Fwith his wife, told the Press
OL,9,FAssociation: "Two guys came on, one
OL,10,Fwith a mic and headphones, one guy
OL,11,Fwhispered to Peter Kay and then he and
OL,12,FPeter Kay shot off down the side."
OL,14,FHe said the audience was told to look
OL,15,Ffor security guards and listen out for
OL,16,Fany announcements.
OL,18,F"To be honest, I thought it was part
OL,19,Fof the show at first," Mr Aspinall,
OL,20,Fwho lives in Bideford, Devon, said.
OL,26,@qD@NOUtD@bO]zD@AOU{D@VO]
