OL,3,CPeter Kay ushered off stage and
OL,4,Caudience evacuated after suspicious
OL,5,Cbag found
OL,7,F"It was a strange atmosphere, eerie,
OL,8,Fjust confused really (about) what was
OL,9,Fhappening.
OL,11,F"But it was alright and everyone was
OL,12,Fcalm and left quite quickly with no
OL,13,Fpanic."
OL,15,FMiranda Richardson, 52, a pub landlady
OL,16,Ffrom Northampton, said: "It was very
OL,17,Fswift.
OL,26,@oD@AOUsD@AOUuD@GO]xD@YOU
