OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F303A1777680175
OL,3,CPeter Kay ushered off stage and
OL,4,Caudience evacuated after suspicious
OL,5,Cbag found
OL,7,F"One minute (Peter Kay's) on stage and
OL,8,Fthe gig is great, then two of the
OL,9,Fevent team walk on stage straight to
OL,10,Fhim, quick word and he's ushered off.
OL,12,F"The staff tells us due to unforeseen
OL,13,Fcircumstances we all have to evacuate
OL,14,Fthe arena straight away.
OL,16,F"Staff helped get people out and it
OL,17,Fwas calm and swift. We heard very
OL,18,Fquickly someone had claimed a bag had
OL,19,Fbeen left somewhere.
OL,21,F"No messing, it was just all out."
OL,26,@oD@AOUtD@AOUxD@AOU}D@AOU}D@bO]
