OL,3,CPeter Kay ushered off stage and
OL,4,Caudience evacuated after suspicious
OL,5,Cbag found
OL,7,FWest Midlands Police said the venue is
OL,8,Fbeing searched.
OL,10,FA spokesperson for the National
OL,11,FExhibition Centre (NEC) said: "Utilita
OL,12,FArena Birmingham has been evacuated as
OL,13,Fa precaution on the advice of West
OL,14,FMidlands Police after a potential
OL,15,Fsuspicious bag was found nearby.
OL,17,F"The safety and security of our
OL,18,Fcustomers and colleagues is our
OL,19,Fhighest priority. We can confirm
OL,20,Feveryone was safely evacuated and that
OL,21,Fthe venue is secure.
OL,26,@sD@_OUyD@AOU
